name: Planetech International
overview:
PLANETech International brings China’s highest technologies to the Americas. We specialize in only special capabilities that have been developed in China, but, are not generally available outside of China.

Products fields include LED lighting, LCD Light Guide Materials and Specialty Packaging Materials.

LED Lighting Special lighting which is designed to better meet the requirements of the U.S. market with higher brightness, warmer colors, and less glare than typical LED lighting currently on the market. Less glare is established using special diffusion films with wide area sources.

LCD Light Guide Materials Special Nano-Imprinting technology for keyboards, keypads and LCD backlights for thinner profiles, higher efficiency and lower cost of LED backlighting.

Specialty Packaging Materials Creating special 3D, 2D and holographic effects for more dramatic packaging using Nano-Imprinting technologies.
